  "original_title": "\u0db8\u0db1\u0dca\u0db1\u0dcf\u0dbb\u0db8\u0dda \u0dc3\u0dd2\u0da7 \u0d89\u0db1\u0dca\u0daf\u0dd2\u0dba\u0dcf\u0dc0\u0da7 \u0d9c\u0dd2\u0dba \u0d85\u0db9\u0dd4 \u0dc3\u0dd0\u0db8\u0dd2 \u0dba\u0dd4\u0dc0\u0dbd \u0db8\u0dbb\u0dd4\u0da7",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Married couple who went to India from Mannar died",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "An elderly couple who went to Dhanushkodi in India from Mannar and fell unconscious on the seashore died yesterday (03) while receiving treatment, Indian security officials say.",
        "On the 27th of June last, the husband and wife couple went from Mannar to Dhanushkodi in India by means of a small boat when they fainted and fell on the beach due to overexertion.",
        "The Indian media had reported that the husband and wife, 67-year-old Parameshwari and 74-year-old Sivan, residents of Murungan area of \u200b\u200bMannar, first died while receiving treatment, followed by the wife after 4 hours.",
        "It is also reported that the hospital doctors said that the bodies of the deceased were severely weakened due to fasting and the bodies have been sent for post-mortem examination.",
        "However, while the couple is receiving treatment, it is also reported that several local authorities have come to the hospital and inquired about the patient's condition, and the Indian authorities have not yet made a statement about the manner in which the last rites of the elderly couple will be carried out."
      ],
